dns latency calculator from tcpdump
(matt.hum@hpe.com)

dump locally
tcpdump -ni ens192 udp port 53 | ./dnslatency

to send to syslog add wrapper and send
tcpdump -ni ens192 udp port 53 | ./dnslatency | sed "s/^/<14>$(hostname -i) /" | nc -u <sysloghost> 514

Optional command line vars
-D      Print Debug messages
-ms     Suppress all requests < 1 ms

